about.summary: Draws Python object reference graphs with graphviz

name: objgraph
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "objgraph" %}
{% set version = "3.4.1" %}


package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/{{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: bf29512d7f8b457b53fa0722ea59f516abb8abc59b78f97f0ef81394a0c615a7

build:
  number: 0
  noarch: python
  script: {{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . -vv

requirements:
  host:
    - pip
    - python
  run:
    - graphviz
    - python

test:
  imports:
    - objgraph

about:
  home: https://pypi.org/project/objgraph/
  summary: Draws Python object reference graphs with graphviz
  license: MIT
  license_file: LICENSE

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - marcelotrevisani
